text: I saw a UFO once I was a SO 9 playing in the street with a friend who's a couple of years old .and we saw a featureless silver disk hovering over the houses we watched it for a few seconds and it shocked away incredibly quickly even as a kid I got angry it was ignoring the laws of physics .we went inside to tell the grown ups and they were skeptical you'd be skeptical to rise .
